1
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,543
Tubuhmu hangat.

2
00:01:26,468 --> 00:01:27,803
Aku lapar.

3
00:01:59,918 --> 00:02:02,546
MOTEL BATES
TEMPAT PARKIR

4
00:02:13,807 --> 00:02:14,641
Kau cerdas juga.

5
00:02:14,850 --> 00:02:16,518
Hangatkan tubuhmu di sini.

6
00:02:16,601 --> 00:02:19,062
- Baiklah. Kita bersama.
- Kau saja.

7
00:02:33,785 --> 00:02:34,661
Selamat datang.

8
00:02:35,996 --> 00:02:37,039
Astaga.

9
00:02:38,165 --> 00:02:40,876
Kalian benar-benar basah kuyup.

10
00:02:41,668 --> 00:02:43,837
Untuk semalam atau berapa jam?

11
00:02:47,132 --> 00:02:48,717
- Itu...
- Mau kamar apa?

12
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,761
Kamar cermin? Bertema?

13
00:02:50,844 --> 00:02:51,845
- Kostum?
- Tidak.

14
00:02:52,554 --> 00:02:53,513
Itu...

15
00:02:55,766 --> 00:02:56,600
Sini.

16
00:02:58,643 --> 00:02:59,853
Sini. Mendekat.

17
00:03:01,938 --> 00:03:03,398
- Butuh pelengkap?
- Apa?

18
00:03:03,732 --> 00:03:05,359
Kursi cinta? Kasur getar?

19
00:03:05,901 --> 00:03:07,694
Mungkin cambuk atau borgol?

20
00:03:09,363 --> 00:03:11,740
Bayar dengan uang tunai
diskon sepuluh persen.

21
00:03:12,616 --> 00:03:13,450
Ayo pergi.

22
00:03:14,034 --> 00:03:16,286
Ada kolam pusaran air gratis.
Rahasiakan itu.

23
00:03:16,370 --> 00:03:17,704
- Ayo pergi.
- Tidak.

24
00:03:17,788 --> 00:03:18,955
Aku suka tempat ini.

25
00:03:21,166 --> 00:03:22,584
Ayo. Kuantar pulang.

26
00:03:22,667 --> 00:03:25,337
- Aku bisa mati kedinginan.
- Kamarnya sangat panas.

27
00:03:28,131 --> 00:03:30,050
- Apa rumahmu jauh?
- Bukan itu masalahnya.

28
00:03:30,342 --> 00:03:33,178
Kenapa kau membawa motor
di hujan sederas ini?

29
00:03:33,845 --> 00:03:36,598
- Lantas naik taksi saja.
- Beri aku ongkos taksi.

30
00:03:37,641 --> 00:03:39,184
Jangan bilang...

31
00:03:39,267 --> 00:03:42,187
Ya. Aku meninggalkan dompet dan ponselku.

32
00:03:42,938 --> 00:03:44,272
Jika aku tak menjemputmu...

33
00:03:44,356 --> 00:03:47,359
Aku akan kehujanan semalaman
seperti wanita gila.

34
00:03:48,276 --> 00:03:51,697
Berpikirlah sebelum bertindak!
Jangan gegabah dan seenaknya!

35
00:03:52,739 --> 00:03:55,033
Bagaimana kalau kau dijahati
saat gelap dan sepi?

36
00:03:55,117 --> 00:03:57,911
Kenapa berkeliaran sendirian?
Kau terlalu berani.

37
00:03:58,995 --> 00:04:00,122
Jika terjadi sesuatu...

38
00:04:05,961 --> 00:04:06,962
Kenapa kau marah?

39
00:04:07,045 --> 00:04:10,966
Siapa peduli aku berkeliaran saat malam
dan bertelanjang bulat di tengah hujan?

40
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,884
Kenapa kau heboh?

41
00:04:14,261 --> 00:04:15,554
Apa kau cemas?

42
00:04:17,389 --> 00:04:18,598
Apa kau marah?

43
00:04:20,475 --> 00:04:21,768
Apa hatimu terluka?

44
00:04:28,024 --> 00:04:28,942
Apa

45
00:04:30,819 --> 00:04:31,820
kau menyukaiku?

46
00:04:36,908 --> 00:04:40,287
Kau benar. Aku bertanya
karena tak mengerti.

47
00:04:40,829 --> 00:04:41,788
Kau pasti tahu.

48
00:04:41,872 --> 00:04:44,749
Jangan bertingkah seolah-olah kau tahu
atau memahamiku.

49
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:47,586
Kau tak mengerti. Jangan berkhayal.

50
00:04:48,962 --> 00:04:50,130
<i>Kau tak merasa apa pun.</i>

51
00:04:51,214 --> 00:04:52,424
Kau hanya bersuara.

52
00:04:53,467 --> 00:04:54,468
Seperti tong kosong.

53
00:04:54,551 --> 00:04:58,763
Aku hanya tong kosong yang tak memahami
bagaimana perasaanmu hingga ajalku.

54
00:05:02,309 --> 00:05:03,894
Bagaimana perasaanmu sekarang?

55
00:05:04,853 --> 00:05:05,812
Katakan.

56
00:05:08,815 --> 00:05:09,900
Kenapa kau diam saja?

57
00:05:10,734 --> 00:05:11,985
Kau tong kosong juga?

58
00:05:16,406 --> 00:05:17,240
Aku...

59
00:05:20,035 --> 00:05:20,869
Aku...

60
00:05:22,037 --> 00:05:22,996
Cepat katakan.

61
00:05:28,668 --> 00:05:29,628
Aku mencintaimu.

62
00:05:31,546 --> 00:05:32,672
Aku pesan satu kamar.

63
00:05:36,218 --> 00:05:37,177
Berikan saja

64
00:05:38,011 --> 00:05:39,763
kamar yang hangat dan bersih.

65
00:05:40,013 --> 00:05:41,139
Biayanya 50.000 won.

66
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,399
Apa? Kau tak bawa uang?

67
00:05:53,193 --> 00:05:54,236
Ponsel juga?

68
00:05:55,153 --> 00:05:56,863
Ibuku saja bayar di tempat.

69
00:05:57,113 --> 00:05:57,948
Silakan pergi.

70
00:06:03,286 --> 00:06:05,080
Sepertinya kau pergi terburu-buru.

71
00:06:05,705 --> 00:06:08,166
Hingga tak bisa berpikir
sebelum bertindak?

72
00:06:12,087 --> 00:06:13,004
Tak apa.

73
00:06:13,421 --> 00:06:15,507
Wajar bagi pria bergerak sesuai insting.

74
00:06:16,049 --> 00:06:17,175
Nyalakan motormu.

75
00:06:25,809 --> 00:06:26,851
Hei.

76
00:06:28,937 --> 00:06:32,357
Jika kau pergi ke arah sana,
ada penginapan murah.

77
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:34,150
Boleh berutang juga. Pergilah.

78
00:06:37,112 --> 00:06:38,154
- Terima kasih.
- Ya.

79
00:06:41,449 --> 00:06:43,285
MOTEL BATES

80
00:06:45,161 --> 00:06:49,666
BAB 5
RAPUNZEL: KASTEL TERKUTUK

81
00:07:09,978 --> 00:07:10,812
Turun.

82
00:07:19,779 --> 00:07:21,573
Seleranya benar-benar...

83
00:07:29,497 --> 00:07:30,624
Keringkan tubuhmu.

84
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:34,419
Berikan bajumu. Aku tak suka dinosaurus.

85
00:07:38,506 --> 00:07:39,883
Menarik sekali.

86
00:07:40,050 --> 00:07:42,177
Bagaimana bisa tempat makan, tempat tidur,

87
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:44,054
dan toilet dalam satu tempat?

88
00:07:44,512 --> 00:07:46,264
Ini seperti kandang hewan.

89
00:07:46,973 --> 00:07:50,060
Bukankah tinggal di sini
terasa seperti hewan ternak?

90
00:07:54,064 --> 00:07:55,565
Kenapa? Aku tak sopan?

91
00:07:56,566 --> 00:07:57,609
Cepat ganti bajumu.

92
00:07:59,152 --> 00:08:01,404
- Di mana Sang-tae?
- Di bawah.

93
00:08:02,405 --> 00:08:03,823
- Jangan panggil dia.
- Pasti.

94
00:08:04,949 --> 00:08:07,786
- Aku tak mau dia bersamamu.
- Kau cemburu?

95
00:08:08,370 --> 00:08:10,538
Jangan pernah dekati kakakku.

96
00:08:10,622 --> 00:08:12,707
- Kau mengancamku?
- Apa pun katamu,

97
00:08:13,708 --> 00:08:14,542
jangan ganggu dia.

98
00:08:15,293 --> 00:08:16,544
Apa dia setuju denganmu?

99
00:08:18,505 --> 00:08:19,923
Kita bisa langsung tanya dia.

100
00:08:22,842 --> 00:08:24,260
Kenapa? Ada apa?

101
00:08:25,595 --> 00:08:26,471
Kenapa tatapanmu?

102
00:08:29,057 --> 00:08:31,309
- Seperti apa ekspresiku sekarang?
- Tampan.

103
00:08:32,185 --> 00:08:34,396
- Bukan, tapi ekspresiku.
- Menyebalkan.

104
00:08:34,479 --> 00:08:37,357
Apa yang kau tahu dari perasaan,
emosi, dan kondisiku ini?

105
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,358
Aku tak peduli.

106
00:08:41,569 --> 00:08:44,989
Perhatikan ekspresi mereka,
dan pelajari emosinya.

107
00:08:45,281 --> 00:08:46,741
Kau harus mempelajarinya.

108
00:08:47,450 --> 00:08:50,286
Jika tak ingin merasakan emosi,
gunakan ingatanmu.

109
00:08:50,995 --> 00:08:53,373
Kau harus tahu kecuali kau mau
sendirian selamanya.

110
00:08:54,374 --> 00:08:55,667
Tidak mau. Kenapa harus?

111
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,001
Kau harus mau.

112
00:09:00,338 --> 00:09:01,840
Aku tidak autis.

113
00:09:02,173 --> 00:09:04,259
- Aku hanya...
- Kau juga bukan anak zombi.

114
00:09:04,342 --> 00:09:05,468
<i>KISAH HIDUP ZOMBI</i>

115
00:09:05,552 --> 00:09:07,929
Tanpa emosi, dan hanya punya nafsu makan.

116
00:09:08,722 --> 00:09:11,349
Menurutmu apa keinginan anak itu?
Memenuhi rasa lapar?

117
00:09:13,810 --> 00:09:14,978
Atau ingin kehangatan?

118
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:18,732
Menurutmu apa jawabannya?

119
00:09:19,607 --> 00:09:21,776
Makanan? Dia hanya ingin
memenuhi nafsu makan?

120
00:09:38,126 --> 00:09:39,210
Kehangatan.

121
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:43,757
Ini yang diinginkan anak itu,
bukan dipelihara seperti hewan.

122
00:09:44,591 --> 00:09:46,009
Itulah pesan tersiratmu.

123
00:09:46,843 --> 00:09:47,927
- Bukan.
- Bukan?

124
00:09:48,011 --> 00:09:50,346
Bukan. Dia hanya ingin makanan.

125
00:09:50,638 --> 00:09:52,390
Zombi tak memiliki perasaan.

126
00:09:52,557 --> 00:09:55,059
Asal kenyang, memotong tangan
dan kaki pun tak masalah.

127
00:09:55,643 --> 00:09:57,771
Kehangatan? Jangan bercanda.

128
00:09:58,021 --> 00:10:01,065
Itu hanya rasa simpati menjijikkan
yang dimiliki orang sepertimu.

129
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:02,567
Jangan asal menyimpulkan.

130
00:10:04,444 --> 00:10:06,154
Aku lapar, berikan aku makanan,

131
00:10:06,237 --> 00:10:07,739
atau kupotong tangan dan kakimu.

132
00:10:28,301 --> 00:10:29,677
Seharusnya dia berkaca.

133
00:10:39,646 --> 00:10:41,648
SAMPO HANYA BOLEH DITEKAN TIGA KALI

134
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:45,026
MILIK SANG-TAE

135
00:10:48,488 --> 00:10:50,949
MENGGOSOK GIGI CUKUP TIGA MENIT

136
00:10:52,742 --> 00:10:53,868
Munafik.

137
00:11:00,333 --> 00:11:03,419
Kenapa dia membenciku?

138
00:11:03,503 --> 00:11:04,587
Sang-tae.

139
00:11:05,505 --> 00:11:07,006
<i>Turuti aku!</i>

140
00:11:19,394 --> 00:11:20,228
Sang-tae.

141
00:11:21,563 --> 00:11:22,564
Apa kau masih marah?

142
00:11:27,694 --> 00:11:29,237
Maaf sudah meneriakimu.

143
00:11:30,613 --> 00:11:31,865
Takkan kuulangi.

144
00:11:33,616 --> 00:11:34,534
Maafkan aku.

145
00:11:41,332 --> 00:11:42,166
Sang-tae.

146
00:11:44,627 --> 00:11:45,712
Sakit.

147
00:11:47,255 --> 00:11:48,464
Itu sakit.

148
00:11:50,466 --> 00:11:52,093
Aku tadi ditampar.

149
00:11:55,430 --> 00:11:58,558
Aku ditampar sangat keras

150
00:11:59,934 --> 00:12:01,561
sampai mulutku terasa sakit.

151
00:12:02,645 --> 00:12:05,189
Aku bahkan tak bisa mendengar dengan baik.

152
00:12:06,774 --> 00:12:10,403
Pipiku bengkak seperti orang tua
dengan benjolan di pipi.

153
00:12:11,821 --> 00:12:14,032
- Aku harus bagaimana?
- Benjolan di pipi?

154
00:12:20,246 --> 00:12:23,207
Di mana orang tua dengan benjolan di pipi?

155
00:12:25,293 --> 00:12:26,794
Benjolannya menghilang.

156
00:12:28,796 --> 00:12:30,006
Aneh sekali.

157
00:12:31,758 --> 00:12:35,720
Kau pembohong!

158
00:12:35,803 --> 00:12:37,972
Pembohong!

159
00:12:38,056 --> 00:12:39,390
Berbohong itu buruk!

160
00:12:39,474 --> 00:12:41,392
Menipu bisa ditangkap polisi!

161
00:12:41,476 --> 00:12:44,312
Dasar Pinokio nakal! Penggembala nakal!

162
00:12:44,395 --> 00:12:46,522
Kau harus dimarahi karena sudah berbohong!

163
00:12:46,606 --> 00:12:49,567
Harus dipukuli! Sampai kapan
kau akan terus berbohong?

164
00:12:49,651 --> 00:12:51,694
Jawab aku. Kenapa diam saja?

165
00:12:51,778 --> 00:12:53,988
Kau diam saja karena bersalah. Sakit?

166
00:13:03,164 --> 00:13:05,917
Kau masih belum makan, 'kan?

167
00:13:06,584 --> 00:13:07,418
Ayo cepat duduk.

168
00:13:10,088 --> 00:13:11,339
Apa kau senang dipukul?

169
00:13:11,965 --> 00:13:13,424
Kenapa kau terus minta dipukul?

170
00:13:13,508 --> 00:13:15,802
Apa kau suka dipukul?

171
00:13:15,885 --> 00:13:17,929
Aku pantas dipukul.

172
00:13:18,012 --> 00:13:19,138
Astaga.

173
00:13:19,639 --> 00:13:22,141
Cepat kemari.

174
00:13:22,266 --> 00:13:23,434
Ayo duduk.

175
00:13:24,185 --> 00:13:25,061
Tidak.

176
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:27,397
Kenapa?

177
00:13:27,981 --> 00:13:30,358
Apa boleh aku...

178
00:13:35,822 --> 00:13:37,657
Apa kau menyembunyikan istrimu di sini?

179
00:13:39,117 --> 00:13:40,493
Pemilik rumahku sudah tua.

180
00:13:41,077 --> 00:13:43,162
Tak heran. Kemampuan memasaknya hebat.

181
00:13:43,579 --> 00:13:44,414
Cepat makan.

182
00:14:03,725 --> 00:14:06,185
Aku ingin tinggal dengannya.
Dia pandai memasak.

183
00:14:08,187 --> 00:14:10,315
- Kau biasanya makan apa?
- Tak makan.

184
00:14:12,859 --> 00:14:14,777
Ibuku tak memotong kaki dan tangannya.

185
00:14:15,486 --> 00:14:17,196
Tak ada yang memasak untukku.

186
00:14:20,033 --> 00:14:20,867
Sial.

187
00:14:46,976 --> 00:14:51,439
RUMAH SAKIT JIWA OK

188
00:15:51,582 --> 00:15:52,750
Kenapa di sini?

189
00:15:53,084 --> 00:15:55,419
Barusan kau mendengar sesuatu?

190
00:15:56,379 --> 00:15:57,213
Tidak.

191
00:15:59,298 --> 00:16:00,258
Listriknya menyala.

192
00:16:02,510 --> 00:16:05,263
Aku mendengar seseorang
bersenandung dari sana.

193
00:16:05,346 --> 00:16:07,515
Ternyata itu.

194
00:16:08,933 --> 00:16:10,184
Itu apa?

195
00:16:11,227 --> 00:16:12,895
Bu Seon-hae tak memberitahumu?

196
00:16:13,396 --> 00:16:17,024
Setelah tengah malam,
di ujung koridor lantai dua,

197
00:16:18,109 --> 00:16:20,778
ada hantu yang bersenandung.

198
00:16:26,617 --> 00:16:28,077
Aku mendengarnya dengan jelas.

199
00:16:28,161 --> 00:16:29,412
Hantu?

200
00:16:30,621 --> 00:16:32,206
Mungkin dia meracau?

201
00:16:32,665 --> 00:16:33,791
Entahlah.

202
00:16:34,667 --> 00:16:35,918
Bu Seon-hae itu

203
00:16:40,548 --> 00:16:43,467
berkomunikasi dengan hantu
untuk mencari nafkah.

204
00:16:44,302 --> 00:16:45,136
Apa?

205
00:16:48,931 --> 00:16:50,224
Dia dukun.

206
00:16:56,147 --> 00:16:57,231
Jangan tinggalkan aku!

207
00:17:00,401 --> 00:17:01,527
Aku butuh kopi.

208
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:06,240
Ronda selesai. Semuanya baik-baik saja.

209
00:17:06,324 --> 00:17:07,241
Terima kasih.

210
00:17:09,035 --> 00:17:11,037
- Dia...
- Mencuci muka karena mengantuk.

211
00:17:11,120 --> 00:17:12,413
Kau yakin?

212
00:17:14,707 --> 00:17:17,585
- Mau minum kopi?
- Tentu, terima kasih.

213
00:17:17,668 --> 00:17:19,212
Bagaimana keadaan Pak Dae-hwan?

214
00:17:19,295 --> 00:17:21,631
Tekanan darahnya masih agak tinggi,

215
00:17:21,714 --> 00:17:23,424
dia juga mengalami gangguan tidur.

216
00:17:26,427 --> 00:17:28,054
Soal tadi...

217
00:17:29,513 --> 00:17:32,099
Kejadian di taman...

218
00:17:32,183 --> 00:17:33,017
Ya?

219
00:17:34,477 --> 00:17:35,978
Kenapa dia mencekik putrinya?

220
00:17:40,983 --> 00:17:42,360
Komplikasi usai pembedahan

221
00:17:42,443 --> 00:17:44,737
bisa membuatnya tiba-tiba
melakukan kekerasan.

222
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:45,696
Ini.

223
00:17:47,365 --> 00:17:49,033
Jika bukan karena itu?

224
00:17:52,161 --> 00:17:54,705
Lalu apa? Maksudmu dia mencekik
untuk membunuh putrinya?

225
00:17:59,794 --> 00:18:00,628
Bukan begitu.

226
00:18:01,921 --> 00:18:02,755
Untuk hidup.

227
00:18:04,549 --> 00:18:07,093
Maksudku karena dia membela diri.

228
00:18:07,218 --> 00:18:10,513
<i>Dia bersikap agresif
untuk melindungi diri...</i>

229
00:18:10,596 --> 00:18:12,098
Mati!

230
00:18:13,808 --> 00:18:14,850
Perawat Nam.

231
00:18:16,102 --> 00:18:16,936
Ya?

232
00:18:19,021 --> 00:18:21,315
Bukankah kau sudah lama
mengenal Penulis Ko?

233
00:18:22,108 --> 00:18:22,942
<i>Maukah</i>

234
00:18:24,777 --> 00:18:26,404
berteman denganku?

235
00:18:26,487 --> 00:18:28,739
Melihatmu sengaja menutupi hubungan itu,

236
00:18:28,823 --> 00:18:31,075
berarti kalian tak terlalu akrab.

237
00:18:32,118 --> 00:18:34,120
Tolong menjauh dariku!

238
00:18:36,247 --> 00:18:37,331
Kalau begitu,

239
00:18:37,832 --> 00:18:40,042
tanyakan dirimu sendiri.

240
00:18:40,585 --> 00:18:43,796
Bisakah kau tak melibatkan
perasaan pribadi dalam masalah pasien?

