814
01:01:21,668 --> 01:01:25,088
O Ji-wang sangat cepat. Dia nakal.

815
01:01:25,171 --> 01:01:28,008
Dia harus menjaga sopan santun.
Orang Korea harus sopan.

816
01:01:32,220 --> 01:01:33,179
Sang-tae.

