01:02:34,949 --> 01:02:36,076
Ke mana dia pergi?

831
01:02:37,369 --> 01:02:38,661
Aku jaga malam lagi.

832
01:02:40,080 --> 01:02:42,123
Apa kau mencari kakakmu?

833
01:02:42,207 --> 01:02:43,208
