881
01:07:37,418 --> 01:07:38,753
<i>Apa dia akan datang hari ini?</i>

882
01:07:40,713 --> 01:07:42,382
<i>Apa dia akan datang besok?</i>

883
01:07:44,008 --> 01:07:45,051
<i>Sang gadis</i>

884
01:07:46,552 --> 01:07:48,388
